<br>
Bards used to be able to stack numerous buffs that wouldn't stack with focus.  These buffs came form Dain's Hammer, BP of the void, and a few other minor items.  These buffs completley and utterly suck BUT for the fact that bards can stack them, thus use them.  Now?  There are SEVERAL 100hp buffs that, erm... dont stack with anything.  With focus lasting 4 hours these days (yay aa ability, wil get into that later), these buffs are never used except by bards.  Now we can't use them.<br>
<br>
Before we were able to stack proc's from weapons.  The most used were proc's of tash from Journeyman's Walking Stick and Orb of Tishan (plus a VT item that I dont have <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ).  Guess what?  Their tash's overwrite eachother now, bards CAN&quot;T stack them any more.  That makes slowing a hell of a lot harder, and in some cases impossible.<br>
<br>
All classes with dots get to stack them.  yay.  Bards dont.<br>
<br>
All classes have an epic they can destroy, and HAVE been destroying for 2 expansions (soon to be another).  yay.  Bards NEED theirs to be bards.<br>
<br>
Bards have the worst dps out of any melee class... inclusing clerics.  We have a target DPS (stated by verant) of 65% of a warrior.  Right now, with full avatar etc, we are at 50%.  I get outdamaged by my level 51 2nd box warrior using weapons i bought for 10k (think i'm joking?).<br>
<br>
Bards used to be able to stack illusions.  This was an extremely minor bonus for being a bard.  The only upside to this was that our werewolf illusion (which gives something like 20 atk and 20 agi) sucked because were would bob and weave, but we could overwrite it with dark elf illusion.  This was nerfed.<br>
<br>
We used to be able to give a tank 120+ DS.  Then this was nerfed to 90pt DS.  Now its nerfed AGAIN to 40ish, WITH the best items in the game.<br>
<br>
Focus items for bards?  nope.  Mana regeneration for bardS? nope.<br>
<br>
They even nerfed bard quad kiting.  How sic is that?<br>
<br>
We have the worst dmg/dly weapons of any class.  We are STUCK with a 16/26 item in offhand.  There are zero exceptions to this.<br>
<br>
Class balancing.  Still hasn't even begun for bards, and it's been 2 expansions and almost as much years.  Now they are going to fubar us up again.<br>
<br>
AA abilities.  You pay 18aa for an AE taunt that hugely betters your class?  Or 18aa for an attack that makes you hit for 1000 PER swing?  Bards get to spend 18aa for a SIX percent increase to songs that are singing based.  Or how about 9 for an ability that increases the range of GROUP songs (not AE songs)<br>
<br>
Planar AA?  We will go further into the shithole in relation to other classes.  Same in relation to Planar Levels.<br>
<br>
Paladins whining about heals and stuns?  At least you DO some damage when you aren't doing anything effective (/cheer 60dmg 40dly weapons that proc 200pt lifetap).  Bards get zero damage and now are reduced to singing AE mana for the casters.  Even AE resists have been nerfed because, /gasp, you still dont resist @#%$-spells with 350+ resists.<br>
